channel.title: WhipScape Development team now hiring
channel.description:
Whipscape
Hello whipscape is a server base of the people. what i mean is there we only do what the people want. what we get in suggestions from the community. whipscape is back in the good old time with old hitsplats there amazing feature of the game all i need is your help. I can do most stuff for the community just need someone to help me durring some stuff. Also i will be running a beta testing here soon hope to see you there beta will be open a week i will list here when beta testing is open.
Features: ~Most skills(never test them all) ~Old Hitsplats ~just like runescape base, but that could change do to what the people want ~Updates will happen fast so i need a dedicated team
Team Members: Host: Salayer(me) Coder: ? Assistant Coder: Salayer(me) Website/Forum Developer: Salayer(me) GFX:Salayer(me)(untill new one is found)
This is a delta base client
Some Graphics:
[IMG]http://i1128.photobucket.com/albums/m485/salayer1/Graphics-1.jpg[/img]
Old Hitsplats [IMG]http://i1128.photobucket.com/albums/m485/salayer1/oldhitsplats.jpg[/img]
We are in Beta testing here is the Client: http://www.mediafire.com/?hsc1jvpzks86ip1 If not working let me know If im missing any info please let me know glad to tell you thankyou for reading.
